OL,3,CTwo in five renters forced to ration
OL,4,Cenergy to afford bills ` Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FMore than two in five private renters
OL,8,Fin England and Wales had to ration gas
OL,9,Fand electricity to afford their energy
OL,10,Fbills last winter, Citizens Advice
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FA third of private renters ` 32%, or
OL,14,F3.5 million people ` struggled to heat
OL,15,Ftheir home to a comfortable
OL,16,Ftemperature, a survey for the advisory
OL,17,Fservice suggests.
