OL,3,CTwo in five renters forced to ration
OL,4,Cenergy to afford bills ` Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FLast month, Citizens Advice warned
OL,8,Fthat this summer's heatwaves left
OL,9,Fmillions of people losing sleep,
OL,10,Fpaying higher bills and suffering
OL,11,Fdeteriorating health in homes not
OL,12,Fbuilt to cope with rising temperatures.
OL,14,FONS data shows that most renters (57%)
OL,15,Flive in properties with an energy
OL,16,Fefficiency rating below EPC 'C'.
OL,18,FThe lower a home's energy efficiency,
OL,19,Fthe harder and more expensive it is to
OL,20,Fheat.
