OL,4,Cenergy to afford bills ` Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FPeople in homes with the current
OL,8,Fminimum 'E' rating spent an extra #317
OL,9,Fon energy bills last winter ` a cost
OL,10,Fthey would have avoided if their homes
OL,11,Fhad been upgraded to C, the charity
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FIt has urged the Government to deliver
OL,15,Fpromised new rules requiring landlords
OL,16,Fto upgrade properties to a minimum of
OL,17,FEPC C by 2030.
