OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FHowever, nearly a third of renters
OL,8,F(29%) said they avoided asking for
OL,9,Frepairs or renovations because they
OL,10,Ffeared rent hikes or creating tension
OL,11,Fwith their landlord.
OL,13,FOf the 30% who had asked, 13% said
OL,14,Ftheir landlord imposed conditions such
OL,15,Fas higher rent, while 7% said their
OL,16,Flandlord outright refused.
OL,18,FThe charity is calling for enforcement
OL,19,Fof the Renters' Rights Bill to protect
OL,20,Frenters from retaliation when asking
OL,21,Ffor upgrades and repairs.
