OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FEmily Wise, energy adviser at Citizens
OL,8,FAdvice North East Lancashire, said:
OL,9,F"Sadly, this is an all too familiar
OL,10,Fstory. Many of the renters we help day-
OL,11,Fto-day say their landlords are
OL,12,Fhesitant to fix the substandard
OL,13,Fconditions they live in.
OL,15,F"Leaky, cold and damp housing is a
OL,16,Fhuge problem in our local area, as
OL,17,Fmany homes are particularly
OL,18,Fdeteriorated due to salty sea air and
OL,19,Fhigh winds.
