OL,7,F"Too often, this is forcing renters to
OL,8,Fspend disproportionately on gas and
OL,9,Felectricity in an attempt to achieve
OL,10,Fbasic levels of comfort, as well as
OL,11,Fhaving to regularly choose between
OL,12,Feating and heating their homes.
OL,13,FDespite this, many of those we help
OL,14,Fare reluctant to raise these issues
OL,15,Fwith their landlords because they fear
OL,16,Fputting their tenancy at risk."
